Name: Runscore
About the game: Currently Version 1.0 (Early stage) Runscore is a survival score based game, about destroying enemies. Enemies give different points depending on the current level. After each level a boss room appears in your way. Destroy everything in your way and get to the Endless UFO mode. In Endless Ufo mode your goal is to get as high score as possible. *4 Levels with a bonus easter egg level *3 Bosses *Achievement
